      "date": "2011-12-30 08:54:49.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.7/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/80cffdac-32c2-11e1-97a7-5254004bbbd3).  Ran 13 tests.  No failures.",
